text: ACME Night was a weekly American programming block. It premiered on September 19, 2021 on Cartoon Network (September 19, 2021 - August 27, 2023) and on Adult Swim (September 3, 2023 - December 29, 2024) , airing on Sunday evenings. It aired animated and live-action movies and series. ==References== Category:2021 American television series debuts Category:Adult Swim Category:Television programming blocks in the United States
